src.infoPage.title: How to create AR business card
src.infoPage.listText_1: In the list below you will find several templates to choose. The design library is updated regularly. If you need to create your own design, please contact our support.
src.infoPage.listText_2: Click this button to create your own business card, and later it will be added into your library collection. You can edit it any time by selecting from the library.
src.infoPage.listText_3: You will be offered two types of preview: AR and 2D mode. AR allows you to see how the augmented reality of your business card will look like. For this just point your smartphone on a flat horizontal surface. 2D preview mode allows you to see the front and back of the business card, which you can print then and give it to your customers.
src.infoPage.listText_4: By clicking on this button you need to fill all fields to display it after on your business card in printed form and Augmented reality format. All fields are required, otherwise the product will not be completed.
src.infoPage.listText_5: When your business card is completed you will be offered to export your version. The format of the business card is adapted for printing. Each user will be able to see the AR mode of your business card by using the AR scanner inside the platform.
